PN,46802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778220037
OL,3,CAre Wales' women on course for another
OL,4,Cwooden spoon?
OL,6,FUnfortunately, recent results suggest
OL,7,Fthat outcome is now more likely than
OL,8,Fnot and it raises legitimate concerns
OL,9,Fover the state of the women's game in
OL,10,FWales.
OL,12,FProfessionalism was introduced four
OL,13,Fyears ago in the form of 12 contracts.
OL,14,FBy 2024, that figure increased to 37.
OL,16,FIt's an investment that was long
OL,17,Foverdue and lagged years behind world-
OL,18,Fleading rivals like England.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778220037
OL,3,CAre Wales' women on course for another
OL,4,Cwooden spoon?
OL,6,FBut results have not followed and
OL,7,Fcritics are becoming impatient. Head
OL,8,Fcoach Sean Lynn is a year into the
OL,9,Frole now and came with enormous
OL,10,Fpedigree after success at Gloucester-
OL,11,FHartpury.
OL,13,FAnd he finds solace in an age-grade
OL,14,Fpathway that is slowly creaking into
OL,15,Faction.
OL,17,F"I know if you want to look at it,
OL,18,Fwe've (potentially) had three wooden
OL,19,Fspoons," Lynn told ITV Wales.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@GpmzD@Spn{D@HO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778220037
OL,3,CAre Wales' women on course for another
OL,4,Cwooden spoon?
OL,6,F"(But) It's very exciting. We've got a
OL,7,Fgood group of youngsters who are
OL,8,Fpushing our senior players.
OL,10,F"You're looking at the under-21s -
OL,11,Fthey beat Italy away last week.
OL,13,F"You're looking at our under-18s in
OL,14,Fthe Six Nations festival - they beat
OL,15,FEngland and came second in the table.
OL,17,F"So all of those girls are coming
OL,18,Fthrough. It's very exciting. We just
OL,19,Fneed to make sure now that we're
OL,20,Fbiding our time. And this pre-season
OL,21,Fwill be big for us as a group as well."
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@BpmnD@FpnrD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU}D@
OL,26,AgO]
