PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778220037
OL,3,CAre Wales' women on course for another
OL,4,Cwooden spoon?
OL,6,FIn this Six Nations so far, Lynn has
OL,7,Fdished out four new caps to up-and-
OL,8,Fcomers, with more likely to come in
OL,9,Fthe final rounds.
OL,11,FThe greatest conundrum across Welsh
OL,12,Frugby is turning talented young
OL,13,Fplayers into senior internationals.
OL,15,FThe game here has often struggled to
OL,16,Ffind the right answers. But Lynn is
OL,17,Fadamant the pathways in the women's
OL,18,Fgame are now fit for purpose.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778220037
OL,3,CAre Wales' women on course for another
OL,4,Cwooden spoon?
OL,6,F"If you're looking at the likes of
OL,7,FJorja Aiono, who I was watching in the
OL,8,FSix Nations Festival last year," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"I'm looking at individuals like
OL,12,FChiara Pearce, and Lily Hawkins was
OL,13,Foutstanding. Sienna McCormack was
OL,14,Foutstanding in the Six Nations, for
OL,15,Fthe under-18s.
OL,17,F"So that alignment with the pathways,
OL,18,Fthe constant meetings I'm having with
OL,19,FSiwan Lillicrap and Liza Burgess is
OL,20,Fjust helping because I can get those
OL,21,Fconnections."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
