PN,46807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778220037
OL,3,CAre Wales' women on course for another
OL,4,Cwooden spoon?
OL,6,FSince Wales racked up a record points
OL,7,Ftally against England, despite losing
OL,8,F62-24 in the last round, a new head of
OL,9,Fthe women's game has been appointed.
OL,11,FNadine Griffiths will take over from
OL,12,FBelinda Moore following the latter's
OL,13,Finterim stint in charge.
OL,15,FThe former is due to begin her role
OL,16,Fthis summer but has already contacted
OL,17,FLynn to express her eagerness to work
OL,18,Fwith him.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778220037
OL,3,CAre Wales' women on course for another
OL,4,Cwooden spoon?
OL,6,FAnd as her tenure begins, Lynn
OL,7,Fbelieves her focus should lie in
OL,8,Fgrowing the women's game as much as
OL,9,Fpossible.
OL,11,FThat will involve increasing
OL,12,Fparticipation numbers at the base of
OL,13,Fthe pyramid, after much of the focus
OL,14,Fin recent years has been on the tip of
OL,15,Fit.
OL,17,F"I'm excited to work with her," Lynn
OL,18,Fsaid of Griffiths.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@_O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778220037
OL,3,CAre Wales' women on course for another
OL,4,Cwooden spoon?
OL,6,F"The big thing for me is growing the
OL,7,Fwomen's game in Wales. And how are we
OL,8,Fdoing that and how are we capturing it?
OL,10,F"If you're looking at under-21s in
OL,11,FFrance, they had an open session and
OL,12,Fthey had 400 girls turn up.
OL,14,F"I don't think we've got 400 girls
OL,15,Fplaying in Wales. So that's where we
OL,16,Fare within the pathway. We've got to
OL,17,Fgrow the game in Wales."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
