OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778220037
OL,3,CAre Wales' women on course for another
OL,4,Cwooden spoon?
OL,6,FThe reality is that the funding the
OL,7,Fwomen's game has received was unlikely
OL,8,Fto yield the immediate results that
OL,9,Fmany have called for.
OL,11,FAnd those results look unlikely to
OL,12,Fcome in this tournament.
OL,14,FThe women's programme in Wales was
OL,15,Foverhauled when it went professional.
OL,16,FIn many ways, it remains in its
OL,17,Finfancy.
OL,19,FPatience was always going to be
OL,20,Frequired. But, for some, it is running
OL,21,Fout.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
